#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:12
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Meath County Council<br> Digital and ICT Strategy 2030 "
"<br>information portal."
msgstr ""

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:14
msgid ""
"Within the pages of this site, you will find information as to the actions "
"of the strategy and our progress on those actions."
msgstr ""

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:15
msgid ""
"The portal is updated every quarter with information, so stay tuned to see "
"how we are getting on!"
msgstr ""

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:16
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr ""

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:26
msgid "Our Digital & ICT Strategy"
msgstr "Ár Straitéis Dhigiteach agus TFC"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:28
msgid ""
"Driving digital innovation and transformation for all <strong>Meath County "
"Council</strong> services."
msgstr ""
"Nuálaíocht agus claochlú digiteach a chur chun tosaigh do sheirbhísí "
"Chomhairle Contae na Mí."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:37
msgid "Evolving Expectations"
msgstr "Ag Súil le Níos Mó"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:39
msgid ""
"Expectations for what IT should deliver have risen exponentially over the "
"last decade. Technology has fundamentally changed how we interact, raising "
"the bar for how Meath County Council engages with citizens as a public "
"service body."
msgstr ""
"Le deich mbliana anuas, tá méadú as cuimse tagtha ar an méid a bhfuiltear ag "
"súil leis ó theicneolaíocht faisnéise. Tá an teicneolaíocht i ndiaidh an "
"chaoi a ndéanaimid caidreamh lena chéile a athrú ó bhonn, rud a ardaíonn an "
"caighdeán maidir leis an gcaoi a ndéanann Comhairle Chontae na Mí caidreamh "
"le saoránaigh mar chomhlacht seirbhíse poiblí."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:47
msgid "Our Digital Strategy"
msgstr "Ár Straitéis Dhigiteach"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:49
msgid ""
"The Meath County Council Digital and ICT Strategy is an ambitious roadmap to "
"harness technology's potential. Following 4 main themes-Digital Services, "
"Workforce, Systems, and Communities-it helps us modernise and improve our "
"services."
msgstr ""
"Is treochlár uaillmhianach í Straitéis Dhigiteach agus TFC Chomhairle "
"Chontae na Mí chun cumas na teicneolaíochta a chur chun tairbhe. Tá ceithre "
"phríomhthéama i gceist léi — Seirbhísí Digiteacha, Lucht Oibre Digiteach, "
"Córais Dhigiteacha, agus Pobail Dhigiteacha — agus cabhraíonn sí linn ár "
"gcuid seirbhísí a nuachóiriú agus a fheabhsú."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:57
msgid "People at the Centre"
msgstr "Daoine i Lár an Aonaigh"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:59
msgid ""
"We are committed to putting people at the core of our processes. This "
"ensures all services are simple, integrated, seamless, and accessible. We "
"aim to deliver services digitally while still offering essential in-person "
"and alternate channels to ensure we leave no one behind."
msgstr ""
"Tá sé de dheargrún againn daoine a chur i gcroílár ár bpróiseas. Dá bhrí "
"sin, bíonn an uile sheirbhís simplí, comhtháite, saoráideach agus "
"inrochtana. Tá sé mar aidhm againn seirbhísí a chur ar fáil go digiteach, "
"mar aon le bealaí riachtanacha ina mbítear i láthair go pearsanta agus "
"bealaí eile a thairiscint, lena chinntiú nach bhfágaimid duine ar bith ar "
"lár."

