#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:304
msgid ""
"This section summarises a selection of Digital and ICT projects delivered "
"during the Council Term <strong>2019-2024.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Déantar achoimre sa rannán seo ar rogha tionscadal Digiteach agus TFC a "
"cuireadh i gcrích le linn Théarma na Comhairle, 2019-2024."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:310
msgid "website"
msgstr "Suíomh gréasáin"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:314
msgid "Website"
msgstr "Suíomh gréasáin"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:318
msgid ""
"In partnership with Corporate, in 2019 a totally redeveloped, customer-"
"centric and responsive website was launched. In the last 12 months alone "
"there have been over 371,000 unique visitors to the site and approximately "
"1.3 million page views! A substantial programme of work was also undertaken "
"to ensure ongoing accessibility compliance on our website."
msgstr ""
"I gcomhar le Seirbhísí Corparáideacha, athfhorbraíodh an suíomh gréasáin ina "
"iomláine agus seoladh é sa bhliain 2019. Suíomh freagrúil is ea é atá "
"dírithe ar an gcustaiméir. Le 12 mhí anuas, bhí breis agus 371,000 "
"cuairteoir leithleach ar an suíomh agus thart ar 1.3 milliún amharc "
"leathanaigh! Lena chois sin, tugadh faoi mhórchlár oibre chun comhlíonadh "
"leanúnach inrochtaineachta a chinntiú ar ár suíomh gréasáin."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:325
msgid "consultation portal"
msgstr "Tairseach Chomhairliúcháin"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:329
msgid "Consultation Portal"
msgstr "Tairseach Chomhairliúcháin"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:333
msgid ""
"There has been a strong focus on the use of our online consultation portal "
"consult.meath.ie/en/ with the County Development Plan and Meath’s Digital "
"Strategy being the first major consultations on the portal. The portal has "
"over 5,700 registered users and since June 2019, the Council have published "
"184 consultations, 10 corporate surveys and 12 application forms."
msgstr ""
"Cuireadh an-bhéim ar ár dtairseach chomhairliúcháin ar líne, "
"consult.meath.ie/ga, agus ba iad an Plean Forbartha Contae agus Straitéis "
"Dhigiteach na Mí na chéad chomhairliúcháin mhóra ar an tairseach. Tá os "
"cionn 5,700 úsáideoir cláraithe ag an tairseach agus ó Mheitheamh 2019 i "
"leith, tá 184 comhairliúchán, 10 suirbhé chorparáideacha agus 12 fhoirm "
"iarratais foilsithe ag an gComhairle."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:340
msgid "CRM website"
msgstr ""

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:344
msgid "Enterprise CRM solution"
msgstr "Réiteach bainistíochta ar chaidreamh le custaiméirí d'Fhiontair"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:348
msgid ""
"The IT team played a pivotal role in the successful procurement, "
"implementation and rollout of a new Corporate Enterprise CRM. This supports "
"back office administrative functions, analytical dashboards, and a Portal "
"for Elected Members. Between Jan 2019 and September 2025 there have been "
"over 240,000 cases processed through the CRM."
msgstr ""
"Bhí ról nach beag ag an bhfoireann TF i soláthar, cur i bhfeidhm agus "
"rolladh amach rathúil córais nua bainistíochta ar chaidreamh le custaiméirí "
"(CRM) d'Fhiontair Chorparáideacha. Tacaíonn sé seo le feidhmeanna riaracháin "
"cúloifige, deaiseanna anailíse, agus Tairseach do Chomhaltaí Tofa. "
"Próiseáladh breis agus 240,000 cás tríd an CRM idir Eanáir 2019 agus Meán "
"Fómhair 2025."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:355
msgid "GIS website"
msgstr ""

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:359
msgid "GIS"
msgstr ""

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:362
msgid "Projects delivered by the GIS team include:"
msgstr ""
"Tá an méid seo a leanas ar na tionscadail a chuir an fhoireann GIS i gcrích:"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:364
msgid ""
"significant assistance on the 2021-2027 County Development Plan (CDP) "
"including interactive mapping portfolio for public display."
msgstr ""
"cuid mhór cúnaimh leis an bPlean Forbartha Contae, 2021-2027, lena n-"
"áirítear punann mapála idirghníomhaí lena taispeáint go poiblí."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:365
msgid ""
"4,569 RZLT land parcels digitised with automated site assessment reports."
msgstr ""
"digitíodh 4,569 fearann talún RZLT maille le huath-thuarascálacha "
"measúnachta suímh."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:366
msgid "spatial reporting services for all departments"
msgstr "seirbhísí tuairiscithe spásúlachta don uile roinn"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:367
msgid ""
"assistance on the Community Fire Safety initiative and Major Emergency Plans."
msgstr ""
"cuidiú leis an tionscnamh, Sábháilteacht Dóiteáin an Phobail, agus le "
"Pleananna Móréigeandála."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:374
msgid "authentication"
msgstr "Cibearshlándáil"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:378
msgid "Cyber Security"
msgstr "Cibearshlándáil"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:382
msgid ""
"There has been a continuous focus on cyber security including enhancements "
"to network infrastructure, SOC\\SIEM, vulnerability and patch management, "
"network penetration testing, email validation, web filtering, cyber security "
"awareness initiatives and the creation of the Information Security Committee "
"to oversee Meath County Councils Cyber Security posture."
msgstr ""
"Táthar ag díriú go leanúnach ar shlándáil an chórais (cibearshlándáil), lena "
"n-áirítear feabhsuithe ar bhonneagar líonra, SOC/SIEM, bainistíocht "
"leochaileachta agus paistí, tástáil ionrachta líonra, bailíochtú "
"ríomhphoist, scagadh gréasáin agus tionscnaimh feasachta, agus bunú an "
"Choiste um Shlándáil Faisnéise chun maoirseacht a dhéanamh ar sheasamh "
"slándála Chomhairle Chontae na Mí."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:389
msgid "Home office"
msgstr ""

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:393
msgid "Covid-19"
msgstr ""

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:397
msgid ""
"As with all organisations we had to quickly adapt to agile working "
"arrangements in a very short timeframe, and the IT department played a key "
"role in ensuing business continuity within the Council and to ensuring "
"delivery of services to the public. This included remote working "
"arrangements, adoption of video conferencing to support remote meetings, "
"increased staff support and managing additional security risks."
msgstr ""
"Fearacht gach eagraíochta, b’éigean dúinn dul i dtaithí ar shocruithe oibre "
"solúbtha go tapa in achar fíorghairid, agus bhí ról nach beag ag an roinn TF "
"i leanúnachas gnó sa Chomhairle a chinntiú agus i soláthar seirbhísí don "
"phobal a chinntiú. Áiríodh leis sin socruithe cianoibre, glacadh le "
"físchomhdháil chun tacú le cianchruinnithe, níos mó tacaíochta don fhoireann "
"agus bainistíocht ar rioscaí slándála breise."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:404
#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:408
