msgstr "Rogha Seirbhísí"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:411
msgid "The provision of numerous solutions including:"
msgstr "Soláthar réiteach líonmhar, lena n-áirítear:"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:413
msgid ""
"Online services for the provision of the allocation of housing units and the "
"processing of the Affordable House Purchase scheme"
msgstr ""
"Seirbhísí ar líne chun leithdháileadh aonad tithíochta a sholáthar agus chun "
"an Scéim Ceannaigh Inacmhainne a phróiseáil"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:414
msgid "The rollout of the national ePlanning Portal"
msgstr "Feidhmiú céimneach na Tairsí Ríomhphleanála náisiúnta."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:415
msgid "Healthy Age Friendly Shared Services."
msgstr "Seirbhísí Comhroinnte Aoisbháúla Folláine."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:416
msgid ""
"Mobile solutions facilitating thousands of inspections across multiple "
"departments in the Council."
msgstr ""
"Réitigh mhóibíleacha chun na mílte cigireachtaí a éascú i ranna éagsúla sa "
"Chomhairle."

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:423
msgid "technology"
msgstr ""

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:427
msgid "Modernisation of Services"
msgstr "Nuachóiriú Seirbhísí"

#: .\tracker_app\templates\tracker_app\home.html:431
msgid ""
"Continued modernisation of processes, technology, devices, operating "
"systems, and software within the Council. This includes but is not limited "
"to implementing and installing a new Hyperconverged infrastructure to "
"replace legacy SAN, virtual environment and backup technology.."
msgstr ""
"Nuachóiriú leanúnach ar phróisis, ar theicneolaíocht, ar ghléasanna, ar "
"chórais oibriúcháin agus ar bhogearraí sa Chomhairle, lena n-áirítear, i "
"measc nithe eile, bonneagar Hipear-chomhtháite nua a chur i bhfeidhm agus a "
"shuiteáil chun SAN, timpeallacht fhíorúil agus teicneolaíocht chúltaca "
"oidhreachta a athsholáthar."

